        "start": 185.76,
        "duration": 2.88
    },
    {
        "text": "got rid of them, he says no that doesn't",
        "start": 188.64,
        "duration": 1.679
    },
    {
        "text": "work, and then with the few that he had",
        "start": 190.319,
        "duration": 2.241
    },
    {
        "text": "left he sort of wiggled the angles and",
        "start": 192.56,
        "duration": 2.72
    },
    {
        "text": "said, well if I wiggle the angle does",
        "start": 195.28,
        "duration": 1.599
